  "title": "HR Executive - Talent Acquisition / Recruitment (up $4500 + Bonus, 6 mth)",
  "description": "<p>✔ Up to $4500 + Bonus </p><p>✔ US Semiconductor MNC</p><p>✔ 6 months (convertible/renewable)<br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><p>· <strong>Working Hours</strong>: Mon-Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm <strong>(flexi / some days WFH)</strong></p><p>· <strong>Location</strong>: North-east</p><p>· Our take: Great exposure in US MNC and also a entry-level position<br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><p>· Partner with internal stakeholders and manpower agencies to source suitable talent locally or regionally.</p><p>· Manage the end‑to‑end hiring process, including job offers, salary proposals/approvals, and salary negotiations.</p><p>· Oversee and facilitate pre‑employment documentation.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>· Degree in Human Resource or related field</p><p>· Candidates with a Diploma but some working experience welcome to apply!<br /></p><p><strong>*To apply, send your CV/Resume to josephyap[at]recruitfirst.com.sg with reason(s) for leaving past employments, last drawn and expected salary.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated with strictest confidentiality. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Thank you.</strong><br /></p><p><strong>RecruitFirst Pte Ltd E.A. 13C6342</strong></p><p><strong>Joseph Yap Shi Hao (R1767577)</strong></p>",
